long_description: it is with these words in our hearts that we sought to create the most realistic real life custom saber experience with focus on bringing together superior craftsmanship and engineering with the latest saber props technology. at sabertrio, we build premium duel-ready custom sabers that are inspired by a certain elegant weapon from a galaxy far, far away. founded in 2016 by three individuals, sabertrio was born out of a passion for a certain galaxy far, far away....and above that, to bring custom sabers to life. starting from a small desk, we embarked on our quest to craft fully functioning duel-ready custom sabers that most importantly, were well made and original in design. today, sabertrio is a company that embodies the premium custom saber experience. we strive to deliver on this promise through open communication, transparency and honesty. we do all these because ultimately, we want you to have a truly memorable custom saber experience with us. lead time your custom saber will be hand built specially for you based on the selections made in this saber configurator.
